content.rendered:
BOSS AIR WATER TRAP

Boss Air Water Trap available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

Water trap for removing water, debris and moisture before it fowls air valves etc.

Semi-auto drain function when pressure drops below 7 psi. Complete with Mounting Bracket.

Includes:

  • 3/8″NPT Female ports
  • Auto drain at 7psi
  • 220psi max pressure
  • Aluminium Body
  • Water level meter on side
  • Mounting Bracket and Hardware

Extra Options Available;

  • Gauge Kit
    • Dual Needle Gauge 200PSI with fittings and 10mtrs of Airline
  • 1/4″ Airline Fittings Kit
    • 1/4″ Airline Valve Fitting Kit Sealant-Less
  • Remote Nitto Add-on
    • Add a remote Nitto Coupling so you can “plug-in” to pump up tyres or use air tools
To view the range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
